import React from "react"; import parse from "html-react-parser"; import Icofont from "react-icofont"; const WhatWeOfferFive = ({ tagline, title, backfont, data }) => (

{tagline}

{title && parse(title)}

{data.map((item) => (

{item.title}

{item.textFront}

{item.title}

{item.textBack}

))}
); export default WhatWeOfferFive;
